HEADWORD: Royally
<hw>Roy"al*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a royal or
kingly manner; like a king; as becomes a king.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His body shall be <qex>royally</qex> interred.</q>
